    <detaileddescription>
<para>MyBookShelf is an open-source Java application designed to help users organize and track their personal book collection. Whether you&apos;re an avid reader or a casual book lover, MyBookShelf allows you to manage your reading list, track books you&apos;ve read, and plan future reads all in one place.</para>
<sect1 id="/app/doc_state/github_reposRepoArchDocGenContext/EliasSchaffer/MyBookShelf/README.md_1autotoc_md1">
<title>Features</title><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><bold>Book Collection Management</bold>: Add, edit, and remove books from your collection.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Customizable Categories</bold>: Organize your books by genres, authors, or custom tags.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Bookshelf Overview</bold>: View all your books in an organized and easy-to-use interface.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Search Functionality</bold>: Quickly search for books by title, author, or category.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Reading Goals</bold>: Set and track your reading goals throughout the year.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
