<title>Installation</title><sect2 id="/app/doc_state/github_reposRepoArchDocGenContext/EliasSchaffer/MyBookShelf/README.md_1autotoc_md4">
<title>Prerequisites</title><para>Ensure you have the following installed:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><bold>Java Development Kit (JDK)</bold> version 8 or higher</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Gradle</bold> (for building and managing dependencies)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="/app/doc_state/github_reposRepoArchDocGenContext/EliasSchaffer/MyBookShelf/README.md_1autotoc_md5">
<title>Steps to Install</title><para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para>Clone this repository to your local machine:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>clone<sp/>https://github.com/yourusername/MyBookShelf.git</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Navigate to the project directory:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">cd<sp/>MyBookShelf</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Build the project with Gradle:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">./gradlew<sp/>build</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Run the Application</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">./gradlew<sp/>run</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
